            "description": "<p>Follow the below steps to download and install EOX Chat App in your smartphones:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ol type=\"1\">\n\t<li><strong><a href=\"https://demo.eoxvantage.com/apk/OXChat.apk.zip\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a></strong>&nbsp;to download the&nbsp;APK file.</li>\n\t<li>Once you have installed the App, you need to enter the Server URL&nbsp;<strong>[https://eos.eoxvantage.com:9065]</strong></li>\n\t<li>Click on&nbsp;<strong>Connect.</strong></li>\n\t<li>Now, you need to enter your<strong>&nbsp;Username and Password&nbsp;</strong>provided by the EOX Training Team.</li>\n\t<li>Click on&nbsp;<strong>Sign In.</strong>&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Now you are inside EOX Chat. You will be added to the default public channel&nbsp;<strong>Town Square.</strong></li>\n</ol>\n",
